    <section>
        <title>Logging Configuration Properties</title>
        <para>
            Logging properties are used to configure how where the Java
            Service Wrapper logs internal output as well as JVM output which
            would normally show up in the console used to launch a Java
            application..  Wrapper Logging properties do not in any way
            control nor replace Logging tools within the Java application.
        </para>
